EN: The situation of water accumulation on the road after the rain should be resolved within two hours.

ZH: 所有问题应在一天以内解决。
EN: All issues should be resolved within one day.

ZH: 药物存放在室内应在25摄氏度以内。
EN: Medications stored indoors should be below 25 degrees Celsius.

ZH: 可在30天以内无理由退货。
EN: Return without reason is allowed within 30 days.

ZH: 请在一周以内确认您的参加意愿。
EN: Please confirm your attendance within a week.

